articles.title: ‘The Bachelorette’: Jenn Tran Named First Asian Leading Lady for Season 21 - Variety
articles.description: Jenn Tran, a contestant from Joey Graziadei's season of 'The Bachelor,' has been named the new leading lady of 'The Bachelorette.'
